            "answer_text": "How to write a leave application for 3 days This is a sample formal leave application letter for your reference. Sample 1 (for office) (Date) To, The HR Manager (company name) (Place) Subject: Application for 3 days leave. Respected Sir/Ma'am, I would like to apply for 3 days leave from xx-xx-xxxx to xx-xx-xxxx (mention the period) as I have a doctor\u2019s appointment for my wife for a surgery. My wife has not been keeping well and there is no one else to stay with my wife at the hospital after the surgery. Therefore, I request you to please grant me a leave of absence for those days mentioned above. I am sure the team will handle everything exceptionally. Please contact me on my personal phone if you have any doubts or queries about the current project. Thanking in anticipation. Sincerely, (your name) (your job position) (ID No.) (company name)  Sample 2 (for school) (Date) To, The Principal/Headmaster/Class Teacher (School name and address) Subject: Application for leave of absence. Sir/ma'am, I am (your name), student of class (Your class and division). With due respect, I would like to inform you that I could not attend school from xx-xx-xxxx to xx-xx-xxxx (mention the period you were absent) due to high fever / cold / stomachache / headache / viral infection. I am enclosing doctor's note for your perusal and record. Therefore, I request you to kindly grant me a leave of absence for those days. Yours obediently (Your name) Class - (standard and division) Roll No: (your roll no.)  I hope this answer is helpful to you. Thank you. ",
